text: FeardotCom is a 2002 British German Luxembourgian American Canadian horror movie directed by William Malone and starring Stephen Dorff, Natascha McElhone, Stephen Rea, Udo Kier, Nigel Terry, Amelia Curtis, Jeffrey Combs, Sven Pippig.
